name: Harvey Street Kids
overview: Kids rule in a place called Harvey Street, where a trio of girls right wrongs, ice cream is always an option, and every day feels like Saturday.

episodes.name: War and Trees / Trade Wreck
episodes.overview: The Harvey Girls go to war when the Bloogey Boys block Tiny from the treehouse. Chaos erupts at the Trading Tree when the girls try to break the rules.

episodes.name: While You Weren't Sleeping / The Secret Strife of Pets
episodes.overview: The kids pull an all-nighter so they can have more fun. When a mystery critter shows up on Harvey Street, a grossed-out Dot wants it gone.

episodes.name: Harveyween / New Kid on the Block
episodes.overview: Lotta faces her fears to save her friends on Halloween night. The girls go out of their way to make a new kid love Harvey Street as much as they do.

episodes.name: It's a Wonderful LARP / My Sectional Romance
episodes.overview: Audrey gets carried away in her first game of live action role-playing. The Harvey Girls battle the Bloogey Boys for the right to keep an old couch.

episodes.name: Campfire Weekend / Girls Just Wanna Save Fun
episodes.overview: Canceled plans inspire the girls to create their very own camp on Harvey Street. A flashback reveals how Audrey, Dot and Lotta became friends.

episodes.name: FruLess / Citizen Cape
episodes.overview: The Harvey Girls do their best to help Frufru make friends in time for her birthday party. Dot launches a business designing fashionable capes.

episodes.name: Cereal / Tiny Danger
episodes.overview: There's a mystery to solve when someone steals the kids' favorite sugary cereal! Lotta works hard to help Tiny compete in a big-kid bike race.

episodes.name: A Matter of Life and BFF / Cheer and Present Danger
episodes.overview: Lotta insists on staying close to the girls after accidentally breaking their friendship bracelets. The girls invent a holiday to celebrate friendship.

episodes.name: Wary Lotta & the Chamber of Secrets / VHMess
episodes.overview: After airing an embarrassing secret, Lotta worries the other kids won't like her. The girls find a broken VHS tape and decide to film their own ending.

episodes.name: The Great Brain Robbery / Can't Purr-y Love
episodes.overview: A life-changing brain freeze moves Melvin to make up for all of his mistakes. Lotta's determined to get a cute kitten to like her.

episodes.name: Elder Skelter / A More Perfect Reunion
episodes.overview: Audrey gets more than she bargained for after taking over for Bobby the Elder. A preschool reunion throws Dot's competitive side into overdrive.

episodes.name: Clinging in the Rain / Raccoon Harder Picture Show
episodes.overview: Lucretia stretches the truth so she can keep hanging out with the Harvey Girls. Thieving raccoons steal the girls' Horn-a-Corn dream house.

episodes.name: Pretty in Pinkeye / The Monsters Are Due on Harvey Street
episodes.overview: Pinkeye gets a makeover and takes his new persona a bit too far. The kids rally when someone -- or something -- tampers with a Harvey Street landmark.

episodes.name: Raiders of the Lost Park
episodes.overview: When Audrey's big sister, Zoe, and her friends take over the park, Audrey needs all the Harvey Kids to help beat the bigger kids.

episodes.name: Dottie Rocket / Weekend at Audrey's
episodes.overview: Dot's model rocket goes up but doesn't come down. Audrey accidentally breaks Lotta's virtual pet, but pretends it's still alive.

episodes.name: Boy Story / Puzzle, Puzzle, Toil and Trouble
episodes.overview: Lotta must infiltrate the Bloogey's treehouse by going undercover and pretending to be a boy. Fredo throws a block-wide puzzle hunt.

episodes.name: Treasure of Sierra Harvey / Babies Day In
episodes.overview: Tiny finds a map to a legendary hoard of buried toys. Lotta takes in three abandoned baby raccoons and treats them as pets.

episodes.name: The Lice Storm / Mission ImpossiBow
episodes.overview: Audrey catches lice from an Avenue kid and thinks all Avenue kids are lice-filled. Dot gets even when The Bow doesn't pick her to be on a special team.

episodes.name: The Fandom Menace / Moby Dot
episodes.overview: Lotta enters a contest to win an empanada date that turns out to be a scam. Dot desperately pursues a rare albino hornet terrorizing the park.

episodes.name: The Cheer Hunter / Dot's Entertainment
episodes.overview: Zoe invites Lotta to join her cheer squad and Audrey gets jealous. Dot becomes obsessed with making people laugh after telling her first joke.

episodes.name: I Wanna Crush Your Hand
episodes.overview: When Lotta goes to the Crush 4U concert, she gets a chance to meet the band but makes a bad first impression and goes through great lengths for a second chance.

episodes.name: Beyond Thunder Dot / 10 Things I Hate About Ew
episodes.overview: Frufru declares that she doesn't believe in climate change and Dot sets out to change her mind. Lotta discovers the popularity of Melvin's video channel and starts a rival channel.

episodes.name: Something's Glotta Give / Afternoon Contrite
episodes.overview: Lucretia plays cupid to try to bring Lotta and Gerald together. When Lotta thinks she broke up the Bloogey Boys, she sets out to reunite them.

episodes.name: Can't Harvey Wait / Bring It Prawn
episodes.overview: Lucretia recounts three amazing tales of Harvey Girls fan fiction. Audrey must partner with Zoe in a shrimp-sponsored sibling beauty pageant.

episodes.name: Hover, May I Board with Danger / Free Gilly
episodes.overview: Audrey as attempted to be on Stu's good side wants to ride his hoverboard. Luckily, she gets a sporty surprise. Billy, the skunk, sings his feelings in a memorable musical episode.

episodes.name: That Thing You Dot! / Where the Streets Have No Games
episodes.overview: A punk-rock preschool rival inspires Dot and the girls to form a band. A hot new handheld video game has the Harvey Street kids obsessed with screens.

episodes.name: Get Rich Quick / Noogie Nights
episodes.overview: The Harvey Girls are getting a special surprise--- the arrival of the iconicly wonderful Richie Rich! Then, things go rough at a game-gone rogue when joy is being collected. Lessons taught during a murder mystery party bring Richie to a close relationship of friends.

episodes.name: Audrey Dreams of Ice Cream / Blame That Tune
episodes.overview: Audrey takes a bite out of what more she can chew when she and her friends grab international ice creams like Harvey Boulevard's cotton candy cones, Italian gelato and Japanese Momo Mochi pops. A fishy jingle brings in an earworm which turns the kids into "songies".

episodes.name: Bad Lot-Tenant / Jet Fretters
episodes.overview: Lotta takes a personality quiz and learns she's supposed to be evil. Tiny and Lucretia offer to get the girls' costumes for the Horn-A-Corn convention.

episodes.name: Now It's Con
episodes.overview: Audrey, Dot, Lotta, Richie, Lucretia and Tiny arrive at Horn-A-Con and decide to divide and conquer, breaking into three groups for maximum adventure.

episodes.name: A Stu Is Born / Ruffspringa
episodes.overview: Richie assembles a team to turn Stu into a social media celebrity. Richie has a sheltered talking dog named Dollar, who doesn't get much of being adorable. Suddenly, when he gets scared by lots of fireworks, he makes new animal friends.
